title: Distorted World - Personal Necropolis (2013) | mp3@320CBR
description:
"Personal Necropolis" - the new single of the Moscow Harsh EBM / Darkwave project DISTORTED WORLD released on the eve of the second album. The main theme of the text was escapism, this is another story that tells about the darkest depths of the mind, which is hidden from the human dream hero songs to find their meaning in life, sometimes incomprehensible to the majority and condemned them.
'Personal Necropolis' - this is the place ...
The single "Personal Necropolis" consists of the original track and a remix of projects such as TERMINAL STATE (Slovak Republic), NORDIKA (Mexico) , RABBIT AT WAR (Germany), ULTIMATE SOLDIER (Russia) and SHADOWKILL (Australia).
